# Commit Message Template
# 
# Format: <type>: <subject>
#
# Types:
#   feat:     New feature
#   fix:      Bug fix
#   refactor: Code refactoring
#   style:    Formatting, styling
#   docs:     Documentation
#   test:     Tests
#   chore:    Maintenance tasks
#
# Subject should be concise and descriptive.
# Use imperative mood: "Add feature" not "Added feature"
#
# Examples:
#   feat: Add flashcard generation from multiple sources
#   fix: Remove 'couldn't find' language from AI prompts
#   refactor: Improve UI spacing and color palette
#
# For multiple related changes, use bullet points:
#   fix: Improve AI responses
#   
#   - Removed all 'couldn't find' language
#   - Increased temperature to 0.3-0.5
#   - Added relationship question detection
